OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1779451869
OL,3,CM6 bridge works to be reviewed after
OL,4,Cconcerns over disrpution
OL,6,FPlans to carry out extensive repairs
OL,7,Fto bridges on the M6 in Cumbria will
OL,8,Fbe reviewed, after residents warned
OL,9,Fthe works would cause severe
OL,10,Fdisruption.
OL,12,FNational Highways said it will open a
OL,13,Fpublic consultation on the project and
OL,14,Fwill try to find ways to reduce the
OL,15,Fimpact on locals.
OL,17,FThe eight bridges over the Lune Gorge
OL,18,Fnear Tebay are due to be repaired
OL,19,Fbetween 2027 and 2031.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
