PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1779451870
OL,3,CM6 bridge works to be reviewed after
OL,4,Cconcerns over disrpution
OL,6,FThe bridges were built in the 1960s,
OL,7,Fand National Highways said repairs are
OL,8,Fessential to keep drivers safe.
OL,10,FThe works would cover a six-mile
OL,11,Fstretch of the M6 between junctions 37
OL,12,Fand 38 at Tebay which would be
OL,13,Fpartially closed.
OL,15,FLocal activists started a campaign
OL,16,Fcalled 'Keep Junction 38 Open.'
OL,18,FMore than 1,700 people signed a
OL,19,Fpetition expressing concerns over the
OL,20,Fimpact of closing the junction.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1779451870
OL,3,CM6 bridge works to be reviewed after
OL,4,Cconcerns over disrpution
OL,6,FOne campaigner previously told ITV
OL,7,FNews Border the closure would force
OL,8,Fher to drive an extra 250 miles per
OL,9,Fweek on the school run, eventually
OL,10,Fcosting #3000 in fuel.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for National Highways
OL,13,Fsaid: "Having engaged and listened to
OL,14,Ffeedback, we will undertake a full
OL,15,Freview of how this important project
OL,16,Fwill be delivered. This will be
OL,17,Ffollowed by a public consultation.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
