FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1779451870
OL,3,CM6 bridge works to be reviewed after
OL,4,Cconcerns over disrpution
OL,6,F"We recognise the importance of
OL,7,Fworking with local communities and
OL,8,Fbusinesses to explore opportunities
OL,9,Fthat could help reduce disruption
OL,10,Fwhile construction work takes place."
OL,12,FThe public consultation will begin in
OL,13,Fwinter 2026 and last a minimum of six
OL,14,Fweeks, with locals, businesses and the
OL,15,Fwider public invited to share their
OL,16,Fthoughts.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
